    auth_contact_admin: 'Nceda uqhagamshelane nomlawuli wakho ukuze uncedwe.',
    instructions_worker_title: 'Isebenza Njani',
    instructions_worker_text: 'Uza kuba nencoko kunye nomncedisi we-AI. Uza kumamela imeko yakho akuncede uxwebhe okwenzekayo.\n\nIsixhobo senza ntoni:\n- Simamela ingxelo yakho ngoko kwenzekayo kwindawo yakho yomsebenzi\n- Sinceda ubeke imeko yakho kumxholo wemigangatho yamazwe ngamazwe yabasebenzi umqeshi wakho omelwe kukuba awahloniphe\n- Senza irekhodi elixwetshiweyo umbutho wakho wabasebenzi onokuyisebenzisa ukuthatha amanyathelo\n\nIsixhobo singenzinto:\n- Asikwazi ukufikelela kwiiwebhusayithi zangaphandle, iidathabheyisi, okanye iilayibrari zomthetho ngexesha langoku\n- Asinayo yonke iimpendulo — sisebenza ngoko ukuxelela kona\n- Asithathi indawo yombutho wakho wabasebenzi okanye icebo lomthetho\n\nNgethuba lencoko:\n- Chaza imeko yakho ngamagama akho. Akukho ndlela imbi yokuqala.\n- Umncedisi uza kukubuza imibuzo ukuqonda ukuba kwenzeke ntoni, nini, phi, kunye nokuba ngubani obandakanyekileyo.\n- Ukuba unamaxwebhu, imiyalezo, okanye obunye ubungqina, ungawalayisha ngexesha lencoko usebenzisa iqhosha lokulayisha.\n- Ungahlala ungachazwanga. Akuyomfuneko ukuba wabelane ngegama lakho okanye nayiphi na inkcukacha yobuqu.\n\nXa ugqibile:\n- Cofa iqhosha elithi "Phelisa Iseshini" xa uziva ukuba wabelane ngako konke okufanelekileyo.\n- Isixhobo siza kuvelisa isishwankathelo kunye namaphoyinti abalulekileyo emeko yakho kunye nendlela ahambelana ngayo nemigangatho yamazwe ngamazwe.\n- Ingxelo epheleleyo iya kuthunyelwa kwi-UNI Global Union ukuxhasa ukulandelela kunye nombutho wakho wabasebenzi.\n\nEyona nyathelo ibalulekileyo onokuyithatha kukuqhagamshelana nombutho wakho wabasebenzi wendawo. Esi sixhobo sixhasa loo nkqubo — asithathi indawo yayo.',
    instructions_representative_title: 'Isebenza Njani',
    instructions_representative_text: 'Uza kuba nencoko kunye nomncedisi we-AI. Uza kukunceda uxwebhe imeko yamalungelo abasebenzi egameni labasebenzi obameleyo.\n\nIsixhobo senza ntoni:\n- Sinceda wakhe ityala elilungelelanisiweyo ngokuqokelela amabakala ngoko kwenzekayo, ngubani ochaphazelekayo, kunye nobukhulu bemeko\n- Sichonga ukuba yeyiphi imigangatho yamazwe ngamazwe yabasebenzi kunye nezibophelelo zomqeshi ezinokuba zifanelekile\n- Senza irekhodi elixwetshiweyo elinokusetyenziswa ukuphakamisa ngamajelo emibutho yabasebenzi\n\nIsixhobo singenzinto:\n- Asikwazi ukufikelela kwiiwebhusayithi zangaphandle, iidathabheyisi, okanye iilayibrari zomthetho ngexesha langoku\n- Asinayo yonke iimpendulo — sisebenza ngoko ukuxelela kona\n- Asithathi indawo yecebo lomthetho okanye iinkqubo zokukhalaza ezisemthethweni\n\nNgethuba lencoko:\n- Chaza imeko ngokucacileyo kangangoko unako: kwenzeka ntoni, bangaphi abasebenzi abachaphazelekayo, kunye nokuba ingxaki yodwa okanye yinxalenye yephethini.\n- Umncedisi uza kubuza imibuzo elandelayo ukuze agcwalise iinkcukacha ezomeleza ityala — imihla, iindawo, ubungqina, kunye nezibophelelo okanye iinkqubo zenkampani ngokwayo.\n- Ukuba unamaxwebhu, izibhengezo, okanye obunye ubungqina, ungawalayisha ngexesha lencoko usebenzisa iqhosha lokulayisha.\n- Isazisi sabasebenzi sigcinwa singachazwanga kuzo zonke iingxelo ezabelwana ngaphandle kwe-UNI Global Union.\n\nXa ugqibile:\n- Cofa iqhosha elithi "Phelisa Iseshini" xa uziva ukuba wabelane ngako konke okufanelekileyo.\n- Isixhobo siza kuvelisa isishwankathelo setyala esichonga amabakala abalulekileyo, izakhelo zamazwe ngamazwe ezifanelekileyo, kunye namaphoyinti okuphakamisa.\n- Ingxelo epheleleyo iya kuthunyelwa kwi-UNI Global Union ukuze ivavanywe ilandelwe kunye nombutho wakho wabasebenzi wesizwe.\n\nYabelana ngale ngxelo kunye nombutho wakho wabasebenzi wesizwe. Yindawo yokuqala yamanyathelo alungelelanisiweyo — esi sixhobo sixwebhu, kodwa asifaki izikhalazo egameni lakho.',
    instructions_organizer_title: 'Indlela Yokusebenzisa HRDD Helper',
    instructions_organizer_text: 'HRDD Helper ngumncedisi we-AI okuncedayo usebenze nemigangatho yamazwe ngamazwe yabasebenzi kumxholo wamatyala amalungelo abasebenzi.\n\nPhambi kokuba uqale, uza kukhetha indlela yokubonisana echaza indlela isixhobo esisebenzisana ngayo nawe. Khetha indlela ehambelana noko ukufunayo ngoku.\n\nNgethuba lencoko:\n- Umncedisi uphendula ngolwimi olukhetheyo. Nawe ungabhala ngolo lwimi.\n- Buza imibuzo, chaza iimeko, okanye ngenisa izinto — umncedisi uyazilungiselela kwindlela oyikhethileyo.\n- Ungalayisha amaxwebhu (ubungqina, izibhengezo, iingxelo) nangaliphi na ixesha usebenzisa iqhosha lokulayisha. Umncedisi uza kuhlalutya umxholo wawo encokweni.\n- I-AI isebenza ngolwazi lwayo olwakhelweyo nge-ILO Conventions, OECD Guidelines, UN Guiding Principles, EU CSDDD, kunye ne-FSC Standards. Ayifikeleli kwiiwebhusayithi okanye iidathabheyisi zangaphandle ngexesha langoku.\n\nXa ugqibile:\n- Cofa "Phelisa Iseshini" ukuvala incoko.\n- Isixhobo sivelisa isishwankathelo esilungelelanisiweyo esisekelwe kwiseshini yakho.\n- Kwiindlela zokuxwebhu nokufaka, kuveliswa nengxelo epheleleyo yetyala ukuze isetyenziswe ngaphakathi yi-UNI Global Union.',
    instructions_officer_title: 'Indlela Yokusebenzisa HRDD Helper',
    instructions_officer_text: 'HRDD Helper ngumncedisi we-AI okuncedayo usebenze nemigangatho yamazwe ngamazwe yabasebenzi kumxholo wamatyala amalungelo abasebenzi.\n\nPhambi kokuba uqale, uza kukhetha indlela yokubonisana echaza indlela isixhobo esisebenzisana ngayo nawe. Khetha indlela ehambelana noko ukufunayo ngoku.\n\nNgethuba lencoko:\n- Umncedisi uphendula ngolwimi olukhetheyo. Nawe ungabhala ngolo lwimi.\n- Buza imibuzo, chaza iimeko, okanye ngenisa izinto — umncedisi uyazilungiselela kwindlela oyikhethileyo.\n- Ungalayisha amaxwebhu (ubungqina, izibhengezo, iingxelo) nangaliphi na ixesha usebenzisa iqhosha lokulayisha. Umncedisi uza kuhlalutya umxholo wawo encokweni.\n- I-AI isebenza ngolwazi lwayo olwakhelweyo nge-ILO Conventions, OECD Guidelines, UN Guiding Principles, EU CSDDD, kunye ne-FSC Standards. Ayifikeleli kwiiwebhusayithi okanye iidathabheyisi zangaphandle ngexesha langoku.\n\nUnokufikelela kuzo zonke iindlela zokubonisana, kuquka Uqeqesho. Kwindlela yoQeqesho, akukho tyala lixwetshiweyo — isixhobo sisebenza njengesixhobo semfundo ngezakhelo zamazwe ngamazwe. Yisebenzise ukufunda kwakho okanye ukulungiselela izinto zoqeqesho zamaziko akho.\n\nXa ugqibile:\n- Cofa "Phelisa Iseshini" ukuvala incoko.\n- Isixhobo sivelisa isishwankathelo esilungelelanisiweyo esisekelwe kwiseshini yakho.\n- Kwiindlela zokuxwebhu nokufaka, kuveliswa nengxelo epheleleyo yetyala ukuze isetyenziswe ngaphakathi yi-UNI Global Union.',
