    mode_documentation_desc: 'Umncedisi ukukhokela kuncoko olulungelelanisiweyo ukuxwebhu ukophulwa okuthile kwamalungelo asisiseko abasebenzi. Uqokelela amabakala, uchonga imigangatho yamazwe ngamazwe efanelekileyo kwaye uvelisa ingxelo yetyala.',
    mode_interview_desc: 'Umncedisi ukuxhasa ekwenzeni udliwano-ndlebe olukhokelwayo nomsebenzi. Sebenzisa le ndlela ngexesha okanye phambi kodliwano-ndlebe — ikunceda ubuze imibuzo efanelekileyo ulungelelanise ulwazi oluqokelelweyo.',
    mode_advisory_desc: 'Umncedisi unikeza isikhokelo sendlela imigangatho yamazwe ngamazwe yabasebenzi esebenza ngayo kwimeko ethile. Akukho tyala lixwetshiweyo ngokusemthethweni — le yincoko ngezakhelo, iindlela, kunye necebo.',
    mode_submit_desc: 'Sele unazo izibhengezo, amaxwebhu, okanye ubungqina. Zilayishe kwaye umncedisi uza kuhlalutya, alungelelanise, achonge izikhewu. Sebenzisa le ndlela xa umsebenzi wasendle ugqityiwe kwaye ufuna ukulungelelanisa oko unako.',
    mode_training_desc: 'Funda ngemigangatho yamazwe ngamazwe yabasebenzi, izakhelo ze-HRDD, kunye nendlela yokuzisebenzisa. Umncedisi ucacisa imibono, ukhokela kwiindlela, kwaye unokunceda uyile imisebenzi yoqeqesho. Kule ndlela akukho tyala lixwetshiweyo.',
